Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Withdraw at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:07.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the Simoun among the Argentine forces today…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:12.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,…was a show of force, to prove to us that they can attack whenever they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that really is what \Nthey’re capable of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.54,Titles,,85,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Eternal Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s really over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war{, I mean}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we can finally live a life\N of simply performing prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does everything feel so bleah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see that other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that grandpa \Nwas always yearning for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The other world…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:31.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I became a sibylla \Nso I could go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria too…?
Comment: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:34.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,…Amuria could be alive as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s no good.
Comment: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mr. Vice-Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, do not call me by that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer hold that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:06.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if it falls and its life has ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:10.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,it can at least comfort someone.
Comment: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you attend the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that’s the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,“It can at least comfort someone,” eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t even do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can no longer protect Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,are the terms that the Archipelago and the Highlands set for their peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was never informed of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:56.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Superficially, at least, we are to be treated as their equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And who should take\N the credit for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,{I would like for you to think\N long and hard about that.}{Wordy}Think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,“War is utter foolishness.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right, Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military governors from Plumbum and Argentum have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, for now—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really the way\N things should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:45.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the girls’ prayers to continue\N in the peaceful skies…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,…that was all I wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with this decision…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way the High Priestess\N was acting just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:11.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are they still here, even though\N the peace ceremony is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard that some of their forces\N will be staying here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,{You know, }I’m starting to not understand what this “peace” is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until they found the ancient Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}their{\i0} comrades were the ones who were dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is what their faces look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,All those faces that we blotted out \Nwith our Ri Maajons…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we didn’t even know \Nwhat they looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:48.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably they didn’t know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the food’s getting cold. Let’s eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Rodoreamon,\N won’t you have some of my fish?
Comment: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’ve been getting too thin lately! \NYou need some nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura, you sound like her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, your feet are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Move those filthy legs outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not that you guys can\N understand what I’m saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? You at least get \Nthat I’m yelling at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have committed a terrible sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you’re taking a shower, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:29.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Yours are… pretty big, eh?\N— What are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Th-They just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:37.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. Because you’re going to become a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless I become a man…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless I become strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I cannot protect\N what’s important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, Neviril told me\N something once…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,To get stronger through\N someone else’s embrace…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not the right way, Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:06.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only when both of you are strong can you really embrace each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I also thought I wanted\N to be a man, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I can pull it off right now,\N without having to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you accept yourself,\N life will be much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you stayed at the Ruins, so how…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that’s what you thought{that to be true}, \Nthen why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place is extremely unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins were the training\N ground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Many incomplete Emerald Ri Maajons collapsed and exploded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Helical Motors…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,…are said to manipulate time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\N space-time was distorted,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:54.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,and that caused the Spring to exist simultaneously in two different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s hard to believe all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are not many things \Nthat people can believe…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:10.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,…when they cannot \Neven believe in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:23.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}was{\i0} struggling to stay close\N to my fallen comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I was trying to escape to a place far away from their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,How… how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I am the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I avoided ever making my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried to escape somewhere \Nfar away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:50.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe… that I’ve been waiting\N for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,For someone to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,To hear…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,…my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,As one of the terms of our peace treaty\N with Plumbum and Argentum,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will be disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is Yun \Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, this isn’t what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:45.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest, disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we worked so hard all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the Plumbish priestesses \Nwill be taking over our duties, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t get it. \NIs this what peace is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perfect equality is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:02.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… I don’t understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,We know one thing for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:11.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The simple truth is that\N we are no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:23.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And just when we were finally able to understand the true meaning of our prayers as sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if Chor Tempest\N ceases to exist…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:31.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,…it does not change the fact that we are Simoun sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one will ever defile our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Chor Tempest is disbanded…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Whaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we will no longer\N be able to fly the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to the other world… \Nwill be closed to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’ve always longed to see that other world, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know you could talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:49.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s been a while since\N we last talked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Comment: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you bless me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s up? Are you sulking?
Comment: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:35.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did something\N happen with Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:41.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you \Nasking me about Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bull’s-eye, eh?
Comment: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:42.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,…has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,She talks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:54.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could always just shut her up with your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:57.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s always about \Nkissing with you, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,{Before }You were telling me about wanting \Nto kiss someone when you like them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you wanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not the way Neviril is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What, you don’t like her anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmpf! You’re just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I’m not—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the…? I feel so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, it’s serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait! What do you mean, serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s not just Neviril, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’ve changed too, Aaeru.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:56.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is Sibylla Aaeru?\N Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it, Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta, you’ll do.\N Please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me, please. Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must fly, Sibylla Paraietta, Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no time to spare! \NWe must hurry! We must hurry or…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door will close on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it will never open again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,“The door?”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:41.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was a member of Chor Dextra.
Comment: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamt of the Emerald Ri Maajon…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamt of becoming an Eternal Maiden…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun is like a maiden herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maiden… wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun Gem reflects\N that wavering heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maiden… drifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forever escaping from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:16.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,she paints the sky…\N with her unending beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please slow down, Your Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}must{\i0} change our country’s fortunes! \NWe cannot go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,If things continue like this{, we will}…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quickly! You must fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the land of hope!
Comment: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Comment: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:19.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:24.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is there something that\N you’re not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I… want to hold you.
Comment: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:36.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,As your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me show you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you run away from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:53.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,and refuse to decide on your sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,these are the consequences.
